videos.headline: Cooke's coast-to-coast basket caps 12-0 South Carolina run
videos.description: Zia Cooke hauls in the defensive rebound then sneaks through traffic for the reverse layup.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Cooke's coast-to-coast basket caps 12-0 South Carolina run) 2021/03/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Cooke fires up teammates with two straight buckets
videos.description: Zia Cooke doesn't need much help scoring as she easily knocks down the jumper and a 3-pointer.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCW Highlight (Cooke fires up teammates with two straight buckets) 2021/03/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Taylor, Allen-Taylor connect on the fast-break bucket
videos.description: Texas heats up as it caps off a 7-0 run with a boost from Celeste Taylor and Joanne Allen-Taylor.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One (Taylor, Allen-Taylor connect on the fast-break bucket) 2021/03/30 EHSEET

videos.headline: Cooke drops in the reverse layup
videos.description: Zia Cooke splits defenders and throws up the layup over her head for another bucket.
